<<.operator-example 1 "[tag[HelloThere]backlinks[]]" "before we begin, run this for verification:<br>â†’ fetches all tiddlers that link to any tiddler tagged HelloThere">>
<<.operator-example 2 "[tag[HelloThere]filter<link-test>]" "same as above, all tiddlers that link to any tiddler tagged HelloThere">>
<<.operator-example 3 "[tag[HelloThere]filter:$<link-test>]" "returns all tiddlers tagged HelloThere that have incoming links">>
<<.operator-example 4 "[tag[HelloThere]filter:$all<link-test>]" "returns all tiddlers tagged HelloThere, should at least one of them have a backlink">>
