<<.operator-example 6 "[tag[WikiText]filter:item $<var-test>]" "returns tiddlers tagged WikiText to which any tiddlers link that also have this tiddler as a tag">>
<<.operator-example 7 "[tag[WikiText]filter:item $all<var-test>]" "returns all tiddlers linked WikiText, should a single one of them have tiddlers linking to it that also have it as a tag">>